params.markdown:
**Overview**

This dashboard shows Incident Audit overview related to the Prisma Cloud Integration.

This dashboard is made to provide general statistics and show the detection of ingested incident audit data.

It contains metric visualizations which provides the total count of incident audits and total acknowledged incidents. 
It also provides information about incident audit by the attack techniques, OS, cloud provider, region, attack type, custom rule, severity, user and type.
It provides details on the top 10 Destination IPs.
It also helps you identify incident audit events over time.

**[Integration Page](/app/integrations/detail/prisma_cloud/overview)**
